`    `printf("Hello, world!\n");

} while (x != 0);

**Difference: while vs do-while**

|**Feature**|**while Loop**|**do-while Loop**|
| :-: | :-: | :-: |
|Condition check|Before body execution|After body execution|
|Execution count|May execute 0 times|Executes at least once|
|Loop type|Entry-controlled|Exit-controlled|

